author: vborja
msg: trying to make nailgun run on jruby 1.1.4.
something weird is happening when comparing two symbols (as if they were
not equal) on project.rb, thus before_define blocks are not being run.
# Call all callbacks for a particular state, e.g. :before_define, :after_define.
def call_callbacks(state) #:nodoc:
# Even when callbacks has a key with the same symbol value than state, (:before_define)
# JRuby.1.1.4 seems them as not equal.
methods = @callbacks.delete(state) || []
methods.each { |method| method.call(project) }
end
